name: Non Fungible Cards collection 11 - How many do you want?
description: Hey lady, come over here, take a look at this delicious watermelon. Very cheap, just arrived from the ranch. Come over, grab yours! It's cheap, very cheap! Take 3 for the price of two! Take one more for your friend, one for your mother. Come over. Very cheap. Only 30 units are available. It's selling out. Don't miss this opportunity.
